reviewText: This series was one of my favorites. Suffice it to say, I am an adult who has never stopped watching cartoons. It is one on my guilty pleasures now that my kids are older teenagers. I have really enjoyed watching it on rainy weekends. It really takes me back...
I was happy to see that the Dr. Katz episodes were finally being put on to DVD but after season #2 it seems to have stopped. Where are the rest of the seasons???
